<a-modal wrapClassName="emoticon"
         :visible="value" :closable="false" :footer="null" :width="401" :bodyStyle="{padding: 0}"
         @cancel="bindClickCancel">
    <a-tabs class="emoticon-tabs" :defaultActiveKey="0" tabPosition="bottom">
        <a-tab-pane :tab="item.title" v-for="(item, index) in icons" :key="index">
            <a-card>
                <a-card-grid v-for="icon in item.value" :key="icon" :title="icon" @click="bindClickIcon(icon)"
                             style="width: 40px; height: 40px; line-height: 40px; padding: 0; text-align: center;">
                    <a-icon :type="icon" style="font-size: 16px"/>
                </a-card-grid>
            </a-card>
        </a-tab-pane>
    </a-tabs>
</a-modal>
